{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, LIME interprets how genes were predicted and which genes are particularly responsible for an AD patient.",
    "The genes identified for AD are ranked based on probability values and are separated into AD and non-AD classifications.",
    "Figure 8 shows an illustration of the LIME explanation from this study.",
    "Another article by Loukas et al. [92] has used speech recordings and associated transcripts from the ADReSS Challenge dataset to detect AD.",
    "In this article, LIME was employed to explain the BERT model that shed light on the differences in language between AD and non-AD patients."
  ]
}